    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
      <head>Scope and Content </head>
      <p>Anonymous scientific manuscript in wrappers, c. 1760, containing notes on the medical
                works of John {sic} {Jan} Baptiste Van Helmont, and on John Webster's
                "Metallographia", Otto Tacher's "Hippocrator Chemicus", Johann Rudolf Glauber's
                "Pharmacopia" and "Philosophicae", and Christopher Grummet's "Sanquia Natura". </p>
    </scopecontent>
